Introduction

Trainee A was a pre-debut boy group that was teased in early 2021, speculated to be affiliated with Big Hit Music. The group had plans to debut in 2022, but unfortunately, their debut was cancelled.

Before this, Trainee A managed to release an original track titled ‘Ain’t No Privacy,’ which was part of their monthly evaluation
